5 types

1. supervised - labelled
a. regression - continuous prediction
b. classification - output is in categpry (spam/not) , (tank/not)

2. Unsupervised
a. clustering - customer segmentation
b. dimensionality redn
c. association rule learning (recommend, buy milk so buy bread too)

3. Reinforcement
agent does action gets reward
a. model based RL - agent plans b4 acting
b. model pre RL - trail n error
c. policy based learning - self driving car
d. value based learning - chess - cal value b4 acting

4. Semi supervised learning - 100 label , 900 unlabelbutbut
1. self training - chatgpt
2. co training 2 - models learn together
3. graph based learning

5. Self-Supervised Learning
Model creates its own labels from raw data (hides part of data, tries to predict it)
a. generative - predict next word/pixel (GPT)
b. contrastive - compare two versions of same image
c. pretext tasks - solve puzzles (un-rotate image)
